Class GFRoundedRectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.draw2d.Figure
      • org.eclipse.draw2d.Shape
        • org.eclipse.graphiti.ui.internal.figures.GFAbstractShape
          • org.eclipse.graphiti.ui.internal.figures.GFRoundedRectangle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.draw2d.IFigure, org.eclipse.gef.handles.HandleBounds, IVisualStateChangeListener, IVisualStateHolder

    public class GFRoundedRectangle
extends GFAbstractShape
    A Graphiti Rounded Rectangle Figure. Most functionality is handled in the super-class. This class only has to define the outline-path and fill-path for the figure-specific painting.
